<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ChocoRocco, handcrafted chocolate assortments and other gourmet confections delivered direct to your door. And while you are opening a box with the \"chocolate\" sign of ChocoRocco Chocolate a smile will appear on your face. Enjoy our chocolate with moderation the first time!</p>

[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space alter_height=\"small\" hide_on_mobile=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1505123810881{margin-top: 0.1rem !important;}\"][vc_column_text]
<h1 class=\"trx_addons_no_margin\" style=\"text-align: center;\">1961</h1>
[/vc_column_text][/trx_slide][trx_slide][vc_column_text]
<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are producing fine quality chocolate products, with a history of 40 years. Our company has developed unique expertise in this industry, offering a wide range of original recipes of chocolate that broaden the taste horizons of chocolate enthusiasts and all lover of chocolate.</p>

[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space alter_height=\"small\" hide_on_mobile=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1505123815658{margin-top: 0.1rem !important;}\"][vc_column_text]
<h1 class=\"trx_addons_no_margin\" style=\"text-align: center;\">1980</h1>
[/vc_column_text][/trx_slide][trx_slide][vc_column_text]
<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our mission is to create high-quality products and develop original and unique quality recipes with complex yet balanced flavours. We have developed high expertise, mastering the art of chocolate, thus becoming one of the top companies in its industry.</p>

[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space alter_height=\"small\" hide_on_mobile=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1505123820913{margin-top: 0.1rem !important;}\"][vc_column_text]
<h1 class=\"trx_addons_no_margin\" style=\"text-align: center;\">1992</h1>
[/vc_column_text][/trx_slide][trx_slide][vc_column_text]
<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ChocoRocco, handcrafted chocolate assortments and other gourmet confections delivered direct to your door. And while you are opening a box with the \"chocolate\" sign of ChocoRocco Chocolate a smile will appear on your face. Enjoy our chocolate with moderation the first time!</p>

[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space alter_height=\"small\" hide_on_mobile=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1505123825281{margin-top: 0.1rem !important;}\"][vc_column_text]
<h1 class=\"trx_addons_no_margin\" style=\"text-align: center;\">2000</h1>
[/vc_column_text][/trx_slide][trx_slide][vc_column_text]
<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We use the same traditional production technology of old times and that is exactly why we have managed to revive the magical recipes giving life to our chocolates which again can travel around the world spreading the atmosphere of miracle. Chocolate makes you happy.</p>

[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space alter_height=\"small\" hide_on_mobile=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1505123829705{margin-top: 0.1rem !important;}\"][vc_column_text]
